### Kontrapunkt MVP API smoke tests (use REST Client extension)
@host = http://127.0.0.1:8000

### Root
GET {{host}}/

### Dialogue
POST {{host}}/dialogue/respond
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "state": {"skills": {"sensual_intelligence": 0.6, "obscura_sensitivity": 0.5}},
  "input": "hello"
}

### Save
POST {{host}}/save/write
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "snapshot": {
    "player": {"pos": {"x": 0, "y": 0}},
    "scene": "Main",
    "skills": {"sensual_intelligence": 0.6, "obscura_sensitivity": 0.5}
  }
}
